<article id="post-107" class="post-107 post type-post status-publish format-standard sticky hentry category-5">
	
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/index.php/2016/09/15/%e6%96%b0%e4%bd%9c%e3%80%8a%e5%be%a1%e5%b0%86%e3%80%8b%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83/" rel="bookmark">新作《御将》发布</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/webwxgetmsgimg.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-118" src="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/webwxgetmsgimg-270x300.png" alt="webwxgetmsgimg" width="270" height="300" srcset="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/webwxgetmsgimg-270x300.png 270w, http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/webwxgetmsgimg.png 720w" sizes="(max-width: 270px) 100vw, 270px" /></a></p>
<p>上面是千秋笔微信二维码，要加的书友请添加</p>
<!--Hermit v2.3.3 start--><div class="hermit hermit-default hermit-unexpand-0 hermit-fullheight-0" auto="1" loop="0" songs="netease_songs#:224273"><div class="hermit-box hermit-clear"><div class="hermit-cover"><img class="hermit-cover-image" src="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/plugins/hermit/assets/images/cover@3x.png" width="80" height="80" /><div class="hermit-button"></div></div><div class="hermit-info"><div class="hermit-title"><div class="hermit-detail"></div></div><div class="hermit-controller"><div class="hermit-author"></div><div class="hermit-additive"><div class="hermit-duration">00:00/00:00</div><div class="hermit-volume"></div><div class="hermit-listbutton"></div></div></div><div class="hermit-prosess"><div class="hermit-loaded"></div><div class="hermit-prosess-bar"><div class="hermit-prosess-after"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="hermit-list"></div></div><!--Hermit  v2.3.3 end-->
<p><a href="http://music.163.com/#/song?id=224273">http://music.163.com/#/song?id=224273</a></p>
<p><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/御将.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-108" src="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/御将-225x300.jpg" alt="%e5%be%a1%e5%b0%86" width="225" height="300" srcset="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/御将-225x300.jpg 225w, http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/御将.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px" /></a></p>
<p>拔神剑，闪寒光，剌苍穹，拒敌寇，威名远扬；上前线，弓弩张，穿无穷，雪世仇，大道至强。<br />
御将显风采，雄师狂飚；君臣贵无猜，频传捷报。<br />
仙侣侠友，立下不世功；佳人美酒，都付笑谈中。<br />
亦真亦幻，情深意长；智兮勇兮，尽在《御将》！</p>
<p>几经努力，新作《御将》和凤凰书城签约了。目前收藏和评论不多，请求友情支持。请你在凤凰书城注册一个帐号，电脑和手机都可收藏，写评只能在电脑上写。</p>
<p>电脑网址：</p>
<p><a href="http://v.yc.ifeng.com/book/yc/3048386.htm">http://v.yc.ifeng.com/book/yc/3048386.htm</a></p>
<p>手机网址：</p>
<p><a href="http://m.iyc.ifeng.com/book/yc/info.wml?vt=5&amp;mid=2XbaoF&amp;bid=3048386">http://m.iyc.ifeng.com/book/yc/info.wml?vt=5&amp;mid=2XbaoF&amp;bid=3048386</a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/QQ图片20161017142358.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-121" src="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/QQ图片20161017142358-186x300.png" alt="qq%e5%9b%be%e7%89%8720161017142358" width="186" height="300" srcset="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/QQ图片20161017142358-186x300.png 186w, http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/QQ图片20161017142358.png 286w" sizes="(max-width: 186px) 100vw, 186px" /></a> <a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/QQ图片20161017142510.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-122" src="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/QQ图片20161017142510.png" alt="qq%e5%9b%be%e7%89%8720161017142510" width="157" height="299" /></a> <a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/QQ图片20161013095319.png"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-123" src="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/QQ图片20161013095319-288x300.png" alt="qq%e5%9b%be%e7%89%8720161013095319" width="288" height="300" srcset="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/QQ图片20161013095319-288x300.png 288w, http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/QQ图片20161013095319.png 707w" sizes="(max-width: 288px) 100vw, 288px" /></a></p>
<p>千秋笔</p>
<p>2016年9月9日晨</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	
