<article id="post-11" class="post-11 post type-post status-publish format-standard sticky hentry category-1">
	
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/index.php/2016/06/12/%e5%8d%83%e7%a7%8b%e7%ac%94%e5%8e%86%e5%8f%b2%e5%b0%8f%e8%af%b4%e3%80%8a%e5%a4%a7%e9%bd%90%e8%8b%b1%e9%9b%84%e3%80%8b/" rel="bookmark">千秋笔历史小说《大齐英雄》</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>千秋笔微信：qianqiubi</p>
<p>千秋笔QQ：290912765</p>
<p>添加时请写明：千秋笔社区</p>
<!--Hermit v2.3.3 start--><div class="hermit hermit-default hermit-unexpand-0 hermit-fullheight-0" auto="1" loop="0" songs="album#:2100335540"><div class="hermit-box hermit-clear"><div class="hermit-cover"><img class="hermit-cover-image" src="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/plugins/hermit/assets/images/cover@3x.png" width="80" height="80" /><div class="hermit-button"></div></div><div class="hermit-info"><div class="hermit-title"><div class="hermit-detail"></div></div><div class="hermit-controller"><div class="hermit-author"></div><div class="hermit-additive"><div class="hermit-duration">00:00/00:00</div><div class="hermit-volume"></div><div class="hermit-listbutton"></div></div></div><div class="hermit-prosess"><div class="hermit-loaded"></div><div class="hermit-prosess-bar"><div class="hermit-prosess-after"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="hermit-list"></div></div><!--Hermit  v2.3.3 end-->
<p>唐末，藩镇割据，民不聊生。公元875年，爆发了王仙芝、黄巢农民起义，建立了大齐革命政权。小说全景式展现了这次起义发生、发展、失败的悲壮过程，用冷峻平实的笔触塑造了众多人物形象。这是一支大齐英雄的颂歌，一首人性涅磐的长诗。冲天掀风雨，秋菊傲霜侠骨风流；奋起挥黄铖，英雄壮举彪炳千秋！</p>
<p>《大齐英雄》链接</p>
<p><a href="http://book.zongheng.com/book/317067.html?fr=pc_alading">http://book.zongheng.com/book/317067.html?fr=pc_alading</a></p>
<p>秋菊诗<br />
摘自《大齐英雄》第五卷第一章 “秋菊凌寒”</p>
<p>秋光映美酒，<br />
今日灞上游。<br />
大齐笑秦汉，<br />
英雄不言愁。<br />
秋菊独凌寒，<br />
花国无敌手。<br />
夕餐上疆场，<br />
弯弓报冤仇.</p>
<p>2014.4.9</p>
<p>注：银杏一梦是千秋笔在纵横中文网的笔名</p>
<p><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/8c1001e93901213f1574b78b50e736d12f2e9526.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-18" src="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/8c1001e93901213f1574b78b50e736d12f2e9526.jpg" alt="8c1001e93901213f1574b78b50e736d12f2e9526" width="215" height="220" /></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	
	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="sticky-post">特色</span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">发布于 </span><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/index.php/2016/06/12/%e5%8d%83%e7%a7%8b%e7%ac%94%e5%8e%86%e5%8f%b2%e5%b0%8f%e8%af%b4%e3%80%8a%e5%a4%a7%e9%bd%90%e8%8b%b1%e9%9b%84%e3%80%8b/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-06-12T18:23:01+00:00">2016年6月12日</time><time class="updated" datetime="2016-06-29T19:25:37+00:00">2016年6月29日</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">分类 </span><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/index.php/category/%e5%8d%83%e7%a7%8b%e7%ac%94/" rel="category tag">千秋笔作品</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/index.php/2016/06/12/%e5%8d%83%e7%a7%8b%e7%ac%94%e5%8e%86%e5%8f%b2%e5%b0%8f%e8%af%b4%e3%80%8a%e5%a4%a7%e9%bd%90%e8%8b%b1%e9%9b%84%e3%80%8b/#respond"><span class="screen-reader-text">于千秋笔历史小说《大齐英雄》</span>留下评论</a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->

