<article id="post-110" class="post-110 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-5">
	
	<header class="entry-header">
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/index.php/2016/09/15/%e6%96%b0%e4%bd%9c%e3%80%8a%e5%b0%8f%e6%97%8b%e9%a3%8e%e6%9f%b4%e8%bf%9b%e3%80%8b%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83/" rel="bookmark">新作《小旋风柴进》发布</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<!--Hermit v2.3.3 start--><div class="hermit hermit-default hermit-unexpand-0 hermit-fullheight-0" auto="0" loop="0" songs="netease_songs#:25703064"><div class="hermit-box hermit-clear"><div class="hermit-cover"><img class="hermit-cover-image" src="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/plugins/hermit/assets/images/cover@3x.png" width="80" height="80" /><div class="hermit-button"></div></div><div class="hermit-info"><div class="hermit-title"><div class="hermit-detail"></div></div><div class="hermit-controller"><div class="hermit-author"></div><div class="hermit-additive"><div class="hermit-duration">00:00/00:00</div><div class="hermit-volume"></div><div class="hermit-listbutton"></div></div></div><div class="hermit-prosess"><div class="hermit-loaded"></div><div class="hermit-prosess-bar"><div class="hermit-prosess-after"></div></div></div></div></div><div class="hermit-list"></div></div><!--Hermit  v2.3.3 end-->
<p><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/25341_1442565688.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-111" src="http://www.qianqiubi.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/25341_1442565688.jpg" alt="25341_1442565688" width="200" height="240" /></a></p>
<p>《小旋风柴进》网址</p>
<p>http://www.junshishu.com/Book25341/</p>
<p>后周皇家传人，贵气直冲云霄。江湖人称小旋风，生性喜交天下客。风流倜傥，仗义疏财。穿越水浒柴进人生，塑造英雄全新形象。</p>
<p>梁山天罡第十，无私掌管钱粮。好汉齐敬大官人，始终看淡名利事。上报国家，下安黎庶。<br />
慨然出征立功无数，指挥义军复兴华夏!</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	
	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">发布于 </span><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/index.php/2016/09/15/%e6%96%b0%e4%bd%9c%e3%80%8a%e5%b0%8f%e6%97%8b%e9%a3%8e%e6%9f%b4%e8%bf%9b%e3%80%8b%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-09-15T09:39:47+00:00">2016年9月15日</time><time class="updated" datetime="2016-09-15T09:54:59+00:00">2016年9月15日</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">分类 </span><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/index.php/category/%e5%b0%8f%e8%af%b4/" rel="category tag">小说</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/index.php/2016/09/15/%e6%96%b0%e4%bd%9c%e3%80%8a%e5%b0%8f%e6%97%8b%e9%a3%8e%e6%9f%b4%e8%bf%9b%e3%80%8b%e5%8f%91%e5%b8%83/#respond"><span class="screen-reader-text">于新作《小旋风柴进》发布</span>留下评论</a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->

