		<span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">发布于 </span><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/index.php/2016/06/29/%e5%8d%83%e7%a7%8b%e7%ac%94%e8%af%97%e8%af%8d%ef%bc%8810%ef%bc%89/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2016-06-29T18:59:34+00:00">2016年6月29日</time><time class="updated" datetime="2016-06-29T19:22:53+00:00">2016年6月29日</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">分类 </span><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/index.php/category/%e8%af%97%e8%af%8d/" rel="category tag">诗词</a></span><span class="comments-link"><a href="http://www.qianqiubi.com/index.php/2016/06/29/%e5%8d%83%e7%a7%8b%e7%ac%94%e8%af%97%e8%af%8d%ef%bc%8810%ef%bc%89/#respond"><span class="screen-reader-text">于千秋笔诗词（10）</span>留下评论</a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->

